{"tid":1117620,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"監獄","createTime":"2019-04-20T20:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T08:59:38.000Z","uid":142854,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"085293060ea8314a6ddbfa79f5b9abfcdf96b104","tid":1117620,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:12:09.000Z","msg":"「啊......我.....」<br />\n「這裡是？」<br />\n<br />\n除了兩邊的牆壁<br />\n似乎沒有其他東西了。<br />\n<br />\n你的面前是一支支的鐵管<br />\n與一道鐵門。<br />\n<br />\n鐵門外是一條走廊<br />\n座列著一個個一模一樣的監房....<br />\n<br />\n與和你一模一樣的「同伴」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們都睡著了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你嘗試用盡全力靠著牆邊去看走廊盡頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n右邊盡頭是一片牆....和僅有的小洞<br />\n<br />\n洞外似乎漆黑一片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左邊是看不完的監房...<br />\n<br />\n即使你已經用盡全力。<br />\n<br />\n「怎麼辦。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA.沉默到天亮<br />\nB.詢問同伴"},{"pid":"25224d80e23ae70ab6084a53d758ccc56fa726dd","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"嗨阿欣"},{"pid":"03e0b3cd5862385fb8dda796917a462bc07d5639","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:23:28.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"42df95f9fa6d0b364231a4986759b410e6b5d74f","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:24:38.000Z","msg":"拆傢具 拎釘同螺絲 通風位開始落手"},{"pid":"e50342e84cf91672711c4afee86b2df872cd54b6","tid":1117620,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e0b3cd5862385fb8dda796917a462bc07d5639","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:23:28.000Z","msg":"B"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:39:40.000Z","msg":"你選擇了詢問同伴。<br />\n<br />\n「喂！」<br />\n<br />\n「喂！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你他媽再吵我明天殺了你！」<br />\n一片低沉的聲音回應著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你靠著牆邊<br />\n不斷思索著你的過去...<br />\n<br />\n從小時候學校被拆<br />\n到不久前的事。<br />\n<br />\n「可惡.......才帶了一包....」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你腦海回到了不久的過去。<br />\n<br />\n那是一個風和日麗的朝早。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「嘿，這包幫我帶去。」<br />\n「好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你按著平常在大街上去著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「停著！」<br />\n十多個警察包圍著你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我...」<br />\n<br />\n啪。<br />\n你被刮了一掌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你被拖回警局。<br />\n<br />\n「我...」<br />\n<br />\n啪。<br />\n啪。<br />\n<br />\n你受到一頓拳打腳踢。<br />\n「啊....啊....」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n「我..」<br />\n<br />\n「我..」<br />\n........................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「噹！噹！噹！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清脆的敲擊聲將你帶回現實。<br />\n一個穿著制服的傢伙拿著鐵棍敲著你的監房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「11001！」<br />\n「早安！」<br />\n「出來。」<br />\n<br />\n你的監門被打開了。<br />\n<br />\n你很想知道發生了甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA. 詢問警衛<br />\nB. 沉默出去"},{"pid":"5c05c945223bda92347b0fcde8f8763036244a8c","tid":1117620,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25224d80e23ae70ab6084a53d758ccc56fa726dd","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"嗨阿欣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:41:19.000Z","msg":"Hi 我是dumbulehedo"},{"pid":"b382de6dde4be5f20a7197c592f94637341e4084","tid":1117620,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:42:45.000Z","msg":"B<br />\n一問陣間又比人打㗎喇"},{"pid":"a47217c6877f7b613f1237330abb55717ec186ac","tid":1117620,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b382de6dde4be5f20a7197c592f94637341e4084","tid":1117620,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:42:45.000Z","msg":"B<br />\n一問陣間又比人打㗎喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:58:06.000Z","msg":"「我...」<br />\n<br />\n心中的不安使你沉默著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「嘿！走這邊！」<br />\n<br />\n你跟著警衛的指示走。<br />\n<br />\n「啊。」<br />\n「新來的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「先去訓示。」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n走廊的沿途是一片片兇悍的眼神<br />\n<br />\n彷彿要將你吃掉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你離開了監房<br />\n外面有一群人在排隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警衛指示你跟著隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你排上了隊伍<br />\n<br />\n排在你前面的是一個魁梧的黑人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要做些甚麼嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA. 視察周圍<br />\nB. 詢問黑人"},{"pid":"d9ffc61d95b4149d6858475475d6f1d3c07a47eb","tid":1117620,"uid":17366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:05:01.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"281062fc5df03767b9f94c89b070d3c4fbe5fff9","tid":1117620,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:08:58.000Z","msg":"C. 大叫力架"},{"pid":"d8ade7f17657e97e0178b6fdeac54859069fe383","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:40:28.000Z","msg":"無得打佢？ 一入來就打柒最大隻是常識"},{"pid":"abfcf0df57552fa879c336b263840a6a214e7a73","tid":1117620,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:40:38.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"6d2c91503aedababe85b59aba5f0d9ee4e69ef60","tid":1117620,"uid":190037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"eefe25a3d940538add642f01e22fc7917685fe0c","tid":1117620,"uid":183117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"C. 同佢隻抽"},{"pid":"e25d7ff6139bf7d105008803b71c07d4c3751d05","tid":1117620,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9ffc61d95b4149d6858475475d6f1d3c07a47eb","tid":1117620,"uid":17366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:05:01.000Z","msg":"A"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:42:52.000Z","msg":"對於看似惹不起的人....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你選擇了沉默<br />\n<br />\n並視察了周圍的環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這個地方」<br />\n「與其說是外邊」<br />\n「不如說是另一個監房吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你心裡默默的念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了可以望見的天空外<br />\n<br />\n你的四周只有監房入口<br />\n<br />\n高牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和一條通道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還有大大小小的守衛在旁邊看守著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數量比犯人還多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨著時間過去<br />\n排在你後面的人越來越多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「跟著前面走！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你向著通道的方向走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來到了更空曠的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警衛指示你們到一個位置集合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n你和其他囚犯一字排開站著。<br />\n各自心中的不安使場內非常清靜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個看似比較高級的警衛進了來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「各位好！」<br />\n「不要管自己是怎麼進來的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這裡是墨西哥的其中一座監獄」<br />\n「我們非常尊重你們的人權。」<br />\n「你們在這裡 每天有12小時的放監活動。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「活動的形式很多，籃球足球，撲克康樂應有盡有。」<br />\n<br />\n「每天有早午晚餐，都是一些不錯的食物。」<br />\n<br />\n「希望你們能盡情享受。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「另外」<br />\n「我不想在監獄內抓到任何違法行為。」<br />\n「所有違法者將會被監懲。」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n監獄長拿出了一根手指。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這次逃獄者的手指。」<br />\n「任何傷人、逃獄者都會受到同等對待。」<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n「放心，只要你們安分守己」<br />\n「我包你們吃好住好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你們有甚麼想問的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA. 我要在這待到甚麼時候<br />\nB. 我是無辜的 放我出去<br />\nC. 沉默"},{"pid":"a01e155c8ded38252d32aa5b93b4976537c0470b","tid":1117620,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"46760882e98fa4c7cd44cbb68fbf60cd31e81994","tid":1117620,"uid":225998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"c5430b0297bc2b2db298b0eeaf4200cc64878a68","tid":1117620,"uid":183117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"4d062b035c5c083b3312f3a786d590e8ba3e882b","tid":1117620,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"0dfc60f7b3c377ebab23501fea2b4f89d6812d84","tid":1117620,"uid":216726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"經常爛尾"}]}